text: Dżesika Jaszek (born 4 April 1996) is a Polish footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Poland women's national team. ==Career== Jaszek has been capped for the Poland national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Polish women's footballers Category:Poland women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:KKS Czarni Sosnowiec players
